text: Eddie Cudworth (11 January 1911 - 19 February 1990) was a Canadian long- distance runner. He competed in the marathon at the 1932 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:1990 deaths Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Canadian male long- distance runners Category:Canadian male marathon runners Category:Olympic track and field athletes of Canada Category:Sportspeople from Toronto Category:Track and field athletes from Ontario
